ndividuals, job requirements and workplace culture.\r\n\r\nFor more information on this leader in its field, visit <a href="http://www.savilleconsulting.co.za" target="_blank">www.savilleconsulting.co.za.</a>\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-327" alt="Shl" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/shl.gif" width="76" height="47" />\r\n\r\nShl, a global leader in talent measurement, offers employment testing tools and employee development assessment services.\r\n\r\nVisit <a href="http://www.shl.com/" target="_blank">www.shl.com</a> for information on their extensive solutions and expertise.\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-328" alt="Insights" src="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/insights.gif" width="63" height="75" />\r\n\r\nEveryone who has ever worked in a team-driven environment understands the importance of solid relations and work methods to get things done.\r\n\r\nWith Insight’s international track record spanning 20 years, we use the Insights® methodology to improve team effectiveness at our clients. It helps people to learn about themselves and others in a practical, results-driven way using colours and fun exercises.\r\n\r\nRead more about this methodology and case studies at <a href="http://www.insights.com" target="_blank">www.insights.com.</a>\r\n<div class="bordered-bottom" style="height: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>', 'Partnerships', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '320-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-16 12:04:52', '2013-10-16 10:04:52', '', 320, 'http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/news/uncategorized/320-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
