(430, 1, '2013-10-16 14:18:14', '2013-10-16 12:18:14', '<p>Mechanical engineer Christian Kaiser has been involved in operational improvement consulting since 2006. His areas of expertise include continuous improvement, process engineering and improvement, and Lean Six Sigma implementations. He also boasts eight years’ research experience in production design.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <h2>Work Experience</h2>\r\n                    <p>Prior to joining OIM Christian was a partner at the operational consulting firm Burger, Kaiser and Associates and a principal consultant at Rethink Management Consulting. During this time he worked on a range of business performance improvement projects, including business process automation, process engineering and improvement, Lean Six Sigma implementations, business process management (BPM) implementation, business analysis and project management.</p>\r\n                    <p>Upon graduation he also spent eight years as senior researcher at Element Six, responsible for product design, the development of material and the transfer of research products into full production. During this time he spent several months working in Sweden and regularly interacted with colleagues on German and Swedish plants. Much of this work involved process analysis and redesign and it sparked his interest in the consulting field.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <h2>At OIM</h2>\r\n                    <p>Since April 2013 Christian serves on OIM’s executive committee and is a principal consultant in operations solutions. In addition to client implementations, Christian is closely involved with the design of new operations management product offerings, primarily in the area of continuous improvement.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <h2>Qualifications</h2>\r\n                    <p>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                        <li>BSc in Mechanical Engineering (cum laude) – University of the Witwatersrand (1997)</li>\r\n                        <li>Graduate Diploma in Engineering – University of the Witwatersrand (2007)</li>\r\n                        <li>Six Sigma Black Belt training – BMG Africa (2006)</li>\r\n                        <li>TRIZ Theory of Inventive Problem Solving – BMG Africa (2006)</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <h2>On A Personal Note</h2>\r\n                    <p>A major outdoors enthusiast, you’ll often find Christian trail running, motorcycling and hiking with his family in his spare time.</p>', 'Christian Kaiser', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'christian-kaiser', '', '', '2013-10-16 14:18:14', '2013-10-16 12:18:14', '', 0, 'http://staging.fishgate.co.za/OIM/?post_type=team_members&#038;p=430', 7, 'team_members', '', 0),
